{
  "stem": "4710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in a fog, the [INAUDIBLE] commanders, those people are going-- going out to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They are not going to work because they are-- they are worried about escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they stayed in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a lot of-- a lot of Russian prisoners of war in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were just strong, grown up people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they stopped [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stop, don't go after him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it looked like he was afraid of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he let me run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was-- that was my second escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and still on the same selection to the next day--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, same selection, next day, Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- on-- on the night of-- on night of [INAUDIBLE], they-- they are from the barracks, which were the children who were selected.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow, they broke out, and there was 20 children disappeared from the camp-- from that-- from that closed barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they dispersed in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next day, when they made the countings, the appel, which was a daily routine in the camp, they had to fill in-- they had to find 20-- 20 or so people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because, you see, the Germans-- everything-- once they had been selected, they said, how many people have been selected?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they have to keep the count of these people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- and the block commander, who was in the barrack, he is responsible that-- should-- should-- for the numbers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when they came to the appel, I was standing-- we were standing in rows of five, and I was standing on a piece of brick or something that I should look-- I-- I shouldn't look so auspicious that I'm-- I'm small.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
